<h3>Thank you to all our contributors!</h3>

<p>The platformOS Documentation is open-source, and we are grateful for all contributions: provide feedback on a topic through the feedback block, open or comment on a ticket on GitHub, or edit content and send a pull request. Find our <a href="/community/contributor-guide" target="_blank">Contributor Guide</a> to learn more about the different ways you can contribute.</p>

{% cache 'contributors' %}

{% assign authors = "https://api.github.com/repos/mdyd-dev/platformos-documentation/stats/contributors"
  | download_file
  | to_hash
  | default: "[]"
  | reverse
  | map: "author"
%}

<ul class="flex flex-wrap justify-between mt-8 list-none">
  {% for author in authors %}
    <li class="w-1/5 mb-8 text-center">
      {% assign avatar_url = "https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/" | append: author.id | append: "?v=4&s=120" %}
      <img loading="lazy" src="{{ avatar_url }}" alt="{{ author.login }} avatar" width="120" height="120" class="mx-auto mb-0" />
      <a href="{{ author.html_url }}" class="no-underline">{{ author.login }}</a>
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>

{% endcache %}

<p class="italic">Contributors displayed here have sent commits to our GitHub repository. The list is ordered by number of commits starting from the contributor with the most commits.</p>
